{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"hillshadeMethod","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNHillshadeStyleLayer(py)hillshadeMethod","title":"hillshadeMethod","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"hillshadeMethod","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNHillshadeStyleLayer"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The hillshade algorithm to use, one of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNHillshadeMethodStandard"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNHillshadeMethodBasic"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNHillshadeMethodCombined"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNHillshadeMethodIgor"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNHillshadeMethodMultidirectional"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnhillshadestylelayer\/hillshademethod"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"hillshadeMethod","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is an expression that evaluates to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"stand